<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">A Pentagon report</COREF> calls for improved intelligence gathering *PRO* to prevent terrorist attacks such as the one against the USS Cole in Yemen last October .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">The report</COREF> also proposes anti-terrorist training for all US troops and recommends a new effort *PRO* to react more quickly to emerging terrorist threats .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">The report released * today</COREF> was commissioned *-1 by Defense Secretary William Cohen .
